## Key source files
- src/models/promptgfm.py         ← main model (GNN + FiLM conditioning)
- src/models/gnn_backbone.py      ← GraphSAGE encoder, 3 layers 128→512→512
- src/models/conditioning.py      ← FiLM: γ,β = MLP(PubMedBERT); h' = γ⊙h + β
- src/models/prompt_encoder.py    ← frozen PubMedBERT CLS pooling → 768-dim
- src/training/finetune.py        ← training loop (AMP, BCE loss, 5 neg samples)
- src/training/losses.py          ← loss functions
- src/data/dataset.py             ← heterogeneous graph dataset
- src/data/preprocess.py          ← graph builder (STRING + BioGRID + DisGeNET + HPO)
- scripts/train.py                ← training entry point (fork-context patched)
- scripts/evaluate.py             ← full-vocabulary ranking evaluator
- configs/workstation_config.yaml ← active config (auto-patched by notebook)

